HWA车队属于一家[[德国|德国]]公司HWA AG，总部设在巴登-符腾堡州的阿法尔特尔巴赫，主要业务为为梅赛德斯AMG开发和制造汽车及零部件。

HWA负责管理梅赛德斯AMG车队参加[[德國房車大師賽|德國房車大師賽]]（DTM）。 1967年{{le|漢斯-維爾訥·奧弗雷希特|Hans Werner Aufrecht}}成立了AMG，并与1999年成立一家以他名字作为缩写的公司HWA AG。在1998年年底漢斯-維爾訥·奧弗雷希特在AMG出售的多数股权给[[戴姆勒|丹拿AG]]，相当于交换赛车运动部门的定制车辆施工企业和部分被剥离并转移到HWA AG权利。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hwaag.com/about-hwa.html |title=About HWA |access-date=2010-02-12 |archive-date=2018-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180502021647/http://www.hwaag.com/about-hwa.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2018年5月9日宣佈車隊將會參加[[2018－19年电动方程式锦标赛|2018－19年电动方程式锦标赛]]<ref>{{cite news |title=HWA AG join the Formula E grid for Season 5 – Formula E |url=http://www.fiaformulae.com/en/news/2018/may/hwa-ag-join-the-formula-e-grid-for-season-5/ |accessdate=23 October 2018 |work=www.fiaformulae.com |date=9 May 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911070113/https://www.fiaformulae.com/en/news/2018/may/hwa-ag-join-the-formula-e-grid-for-season-5/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並公佈了車手名單有[[德國房車大師賽|德國房車大師賽]]冠軍<ref>{{cite news |title=Gary Paffett wins DTM title in spite of René Rast’s six-pack |url=https://www.dtm.com/en/news/gary-paffett-wins-dtm-title-spite-ren-rast-s-six-pack-2018-10-14.html |accessdate=23 October 2018 |work=DTM.com |date=14 October 2018 |language=en}}</ref>{{le|加里·帕费特|Gary Paffett}}<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kalinauckas |first1=Alex |title=HWA announces Paffett as first FE driver, reveals 2018/19 livery |url=https://www.autosport.com/fe/news/139254/hwa-reveals-paffett-as-first-fe-driver |accessdate=23 October 2018 |work=Autosport.com |date=8 October 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023234343/https://www.autosport.com/fe/news/139254/hwa-reveals-paffett-as-first-fe-driver |dead-url=no }}</ref>和前[[邁凱倫車隊|邁凱倫車隊]][[一級方程式|一級方程式]]車手[[斯托弗·范多恩|斯托弗·范多恩]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Edmondson |first1=Laurence |title=Vandoorne confirms Formula E move in 2019 |url=http://www.espn.com/f1/story/_/id/24987255/stoffel-vandoorne-confirms-formula-e-move-2019 |accessdate=23 October 2018 |work=ESPN.com |date=15 October 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410202302/http://www.espn.com/f1/story/_/id/24987255/stoffel-vandoorne-confirms-formula-e-move-2019 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年10月，HWA車隊成為參加[[国际汽联三级方程式锦标赛|国际汽联三级方程式锦标赛]]首個賽季的車隊之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.autosport.com/f3/news/139333/mercedes-partner-hwa-for-new-fia-f3-series|title=FIA Formula 3 2019 team list revealed, including Mercedes ally HWA|last=Simmons|first=Marcus|work=[[Autosport|Autosport]]|publisher=[[Motorsport_Network|Motorsport Network]]|date=October 12, 2018|accessdate=January 21, 2019|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417231743/https://www.autosport.com/f3/news/139333/mercedes-partner-hwa-for-new-fia-f3-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2019年1月，車隊與{{le|阿登國際|Arden International}}達成了[[二级方程式锦标赛|國際汽聯二級方程式錦標賽]]的合作夥伴關係。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arden-motorsport.com/press/arden-international-motorsport-and-hwa-racelab-to-initiate-formula-2-co-operation|title=Arden International Motorsport and HWA RACELAB to initiate Formula 2 co-operation|date=January 21, 2019|accessdate=January 21, 2019|archive-date=2019-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716151134/https://www.arden-motorsport.com/press/arden-international-motorsport-and-hwa-racelab-to-initiate-formula-2-co-operation|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年10月16日，車隊宣佈將會由阿登國際車隊退出[[2020年二级方程式锦标赛|2020年二级方程式锦标赛]]，將由HWA車隊接管參賽資格。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.crash.net/f2/news/931359/1/hwa-takes-over-arden-s-formula-2-entry-2020|title=Redirect Notice|last=|first=|date=|website=www.google.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016204609/https://www.crash.net/f2/news/931359/1/hwa-takes-over-arden-s-formula-2-entry-2020|archive-date=2019-10-16|access-date=2019-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨後，車隊公佈了阿登國際車隊的現任車手{{le|阿尔乔姆·马尔克洛夫|Artem Markelov}}成為車隊參加二级方程式锦标赛的首位車手。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fiaformula2.com/News-Room/News/2019/11_November/Markelov-signs-with-F2-newcomers-HWA-RACELAB/|title=MARKELOV SIGNS WITH F2 NEWCOMERS HWA RACELAB|date=November 22, 2019|accessdate=November 22, 2019|archive-date=2019-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191127231917/http://www.fiaformula2.com/News-Room/News/2019/11_November/Markelov-signs-with-F2-newcomers-HWA-RACELAB/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

